name: src/ESComplexModule.js
ESComplexModule
description: Provides a runtime to invoke ESComplexModule plugins for processing / metrics calculations of independent modules.

params.name: options
params.description:
module options including user plugins to load including:

(boolean)         loadDefaultPlugins - When false ESComplexModule will not load any default plugins.
(Array<Object>)   plugins - A list of ESComplexModule plugins that have already been instantiated.
params.descriptionRaw:
module options including user plugins to load including:


name: _plugins
description: Provides dispatch methods to all module plugins.
descriptionRaw: Provides dispatch methods to all module plugins.

name: analyze
description: Processes the given ast and calculates metrics via plugins.

name: analyzeAsync
description: Wraps in a Promise processing the given ast and calculates metrics via plugins.

name: src/Plugins.js
Plugins
description:

properly manage and or create initial data that are processed by the plugins.

name: onConfigure
description:
Initializes the default `settings` object hash and then invokes the `onConfigure` plugin callback for all loaded
plugins.

name: onLoadSyntax
description:
